      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768986071523,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "V1:\n- Assuming a sale call is\nbetween 15-30min, we upload\nthe whole audio\n- Audio is upload in a\n\"stream\" maner so it doesn't\ntakes the whole RAM\n\nV2:\n- To handle large file and\naudio call, this service who\nneed to upload file chunk by\nchunk",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "V1:\n- Assuming a sale call is between 15-30min, we upload the whole audio\n- Audio is upload in a \"stream\" maner so it doesn't takes the whole RAM\n\nV2:\n- To handle large file and audio call, this service who need to upload file chunk by chunk",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
