      "text": "V1:\n- Validate the audio format\n(wav, mp3, mpeg)\n- Check if audio is not\nempty or too long\n\nV2:\n- If a file is too large,\nthis service would be\nresponsible to chunk it (By\nduration or pause in speech)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "V1:\n- Validate the audio format (wav, mp3, mpeg)\n- Check if audio is not empty or too long\n\nV2:\n- If a file is too large, this service would be responsible to chunk it (By duration or pause in speech)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ywDpanp3McS9omsvyvgfz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -11000,
      "y": 1100,
      "width": 400.00000000000057,
      "height": 214.56931147831892,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "JJ-XeOHWj195p_7ZRNpI8",
      "index": "bDv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2028900062,
      "version": 912,
      "versionNonce": 428329401,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1769040081009,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The Process Service is core system of WaaS, it\nresponsible for hosting Whisper and transcribe the\ngiven audio file.\nIt also uploads the trasnscript to the s3.\n\nThis service uses FastAPI + FastStream to easily\nsubscribe to a kafka topic and parse message\n\nThe kafka queue allow us to ease load on the\nmodel. The ProcessService will impose it's process\nrythm even in a peak usage\n",
      "fontSize": 14.304620765221262,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The Process Service is core system of WaaS, it responsible for hosting Whisper and transcribe the given audio file.\nIt also uploads the trasnscript to the s3.\n\nThis service uses FastAPI + FastStream to easily subscribe to a kafka topic and parse message\n\nThe kafka queue allow us to ease load on the model. The ProcessService will impose it's process rythm even in a peak usage\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
